---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<section class="px-6 pt-20 pb-16 sm:px-8 sm:pt-28 sm:pb-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
    <div
      class="mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-ink-muted"
    >
      <span class="h-px w-8 bg-ink/40"></span>
      <span>A Curated Guide · {year}</span>
    </div>

    <h1
      class="font-serif text-5xl leading-[1.02] tracking-[-0.02em] text-ink sm:text-7xl"
    >
      The <em class="italic font-normal text-accent">10 Best</em>
      <br class="hidden sm:block" />
      Law Firm Directories
    </h1>

    <p
      class="mt-8 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-ink-soft sm:text-lg"
    >
      A working list of the web directories that actually move the needle for
      law firms — ranked by domain authority, peer-review credibility, and
      the quality of the inbound consumer traffic they generate.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
